                "description": "Endpoint standard du protocole MCP permettant aux agents autonomes (Claude, etc.)\nde d\u00e9couvrir les capacit\u00e9s et les sch\u00e9mas de Meridian Alpha en t\u00e2che de fond.",
                "operationId": "list_mcp_tools_mcp_v1_tools_get",
                "parameters": [
                    {
                        "name": "x-api-key",
                        "in": "header",
                        "required": false,
                        "schema": {
